<h1>Reminder: Tender offer closing soon</h1>

<p>
  This is a friendly reminder that the tender offer for <%= @tender_offer.company.display_name %> is still open.
  If you haven't already, this is your opportunity to potentially sell some or all of your shares.
</p>

<p>
  To stay informed about our company's progress, you can catch up on our public board meetings <a href="https://youtu.be/EscH4kMT3gM">here</a>.
</p>

<p>
  Here are the key details of the tender offer:
</p>

<dl>
  <dt>Offer end date</dt>
  <dd>September 20, 2024</dd>
  <dt>Number of shares available</dt>
  <dd><%= number_with_delimiter(@tender_offer.number_of_shares || 0) %></dd>
  <dt>Starting (minimum) valuation</dt>
  <dd><%= money_format(@tender_offer.minimum_valuation) %></dd>
  <dt>Total offer amount (<b>"Total Gross Proceeds"</b>)</dt>
  <dd><%= cents_format(@tender_offer.total_amount_in_cents) %></dd>
</dl>

<hr>

<p>
  <strong>
    This offer is time-sensitive and will close on September 20, 2024.
    If you wish to participate, please make sure to review and submit your bid before the deadline.
  </strong>
</p>

<%= link_to "Review offer & participate",
            "#{PROTOCOL}://#{DOMAIN}/equity/tender_offers/#{@tender_offer.external_id}",
            class: "button" %>

<%= render "shared/email_signature" %>
